description:
In this week's mini-episode, Kate and Doree answer a listener question about what small things they do to ease their anxiety on a daily basis. They also hear from a pair of pen pals who separately wrote/called into the show with questions about hand cream and removing makeup, and get a listener recommendation for a great body positivity follow on Instagram. 

For more info, visit forever35podcast.com. To leave a voicemail, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
